setttings.fftsettings: 256 64 512 for melbands, spectral shape, and sines, 256 64 256 for everything else at the small size. medium is 512 64 1024 for everything and when analyzing the whole sample it's 2048 128 2048 for everything (all relative to a 44.1k sample rate)
setttings.numframes: 256, 4410, whole sample (relative to a 44.1k sample rate)
setttings.descriptors: mean of loudness, deriv of loudness, mean of centroid, deriv of centroid, mean of flatness, deriv of flatness, mean of pitch, pitch confidence, 40 melbands (for spectral compensation), 13 mfccs + stats, 32 sinusoids (as frequency/gain pairs)
setttings.comment: 8d of descriptors for nearest neighbor matching, and then loudness and 40 melbands for loudness/spectral compensation, 13 mfccs + stats for classificaiton/regression. and 32 frequency/gain pairs from sinusoidal analysis, also includes normalized and robust scaled versions of each set of data and time frame
